snippet.title: The Inn Between: Trailer
snippet.description:
The Inn Between is a modern fantasy BL / Yaoi Visual Novel.

With character art by Xian Jin, Backgrounds by Vui Huynh and music by Efe Tozan. 

Trailer created by KotoriMWorks

Now on Kickstarter! 

https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/catslilypad/the-inn-between-visual-novel?ref=d813pf
